T1  - FINANCIAL RISK AND UNEMPLOYMENT
AU  - Eckstein, Zvi
AU  - Setty, Ofer
AU  - Weiss, David
Y1  - 2019/05/01
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2019/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12360
