T1  - IDIOSYNCRATIC RISK, AGGREGATE RISK, AND THE WELFARE EFFECTS OF SOCIAL SECURITY
AU  - Harenberg, Daniel
AU  - Ludwig, Alexander
Y1  - 2019/05/01
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2019/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12365
T2  - International Economic Review
